      "qualifiedName": "withAzureStorageExplorer",
      "description": "Adds an Azure Storage Explorer instance to a Blob storage resource.",
      "remarks": "Add an Azure Storage Explorer container to the application model and reference it in a .NET project.\n```\nvar builder = DistributedApplication.CreateBuilder(args);\nvar storage = builder.AddAzureStorage(\"storage\")\n.RunAsEmulator(azurite =>\n{\nazurite\n.WithBlobPort(27000)\n.WithQueuePort(27001)\n.WithTablePort(27002);\n});\nvar blobs = storage.AddBlobs(\"blobs\")\n.WithAzureStorageExplorer();\nbuilder.Build().Run();\n```",
      "returns": "A reference to the `IResourceBuilder`1`.",
      "kind": "Method",
      "signature": "withAzureStorageExplorer(configureContainer?: (obj: AzureStorageExplorerResource) => Promise<void>, name?: string): AzureBlobStorageResource",
